Name: Battle Royale Survival
About the game: Battle Royale Survival is a Battle Royale game set in a cartoon styled world. Fight against players or bots. There can be a maximum of 20 players per game. Fight up to 99 bots. Drops will supply the battlefield. Choose from one of the 5 characters available and get in on the action. Features: * Choice of 5 characters. * A Battle Royale map. * Bots. * Drop system.
